VIOLET DOCK PORT, INC., LLC, petitioner,
v.
ST. BERNARD PORT, HARBOR, & TERMINAL DISTRICT. No. 17-1656. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 15, 2018.

Motion of NFIB Small Business Legal Center, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Louisiana denied.
